    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CarX Street Drift Cars opens the doors to a world of cars primed for drifting at top speeds. In this release, you'll get three cars, each crafted for perfect skidding during turns.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This set includes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >S18 Special Edition - This car is perfect for mountainous terrain. The 21 Tribe club can't wait for you to challenge them.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SI5 Special Edition - This car is perfect for drifting in the confined spaces of parking lots. The Savage club is ready to compete with this car.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >DX7 Special Edition - This car is perfect for drifting on narrow city streets. Ray Rhompson and the Drift United club are waiting for you to show up in this car.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition, you'll get a currency pack to help you fine-tune your new cars.</p>",
